                Creative Companion Calls: A process that feels more like an
                artist collaboration than a business transaction. Think of each
                site as a collaborative a rtwork: your client brings the
                inspiration, and you bring the technical brushstrokes
              </li>
              <li>
                “Palette Picker” Questionnaire: Help clients choose colors based
                on their work and style.
              </li>
              <li>
                Microinteractions: Hover animations like brush strokes
                appearing, cursor turning into a paintbrush, loading screens
                with small “art studio” metaphors
              </li>
            </ul>
            <ButtonProps btn1="see how LC works" btn1Link="/#how-it-works" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
